layer plays pro ball outside the NBA.|first=Larry|last=Coon|authorlink=Larry Coon|accessdate=April 13, 2014}}</ref> This list includes draft rights that were acquired from trades with other teams.\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:left; font-size:90%;\"\n! style=\"{{NBA color cell|Houston Rockets}};\"|Draft\n! style=\"{{NBA color cell|Houston Rockets}};\"|Round\n! style=\"{{NBA color cell|Houston Rockets}};\"|Pick\n! style=\"{{NBA color cell|Houston Rockets}};\"|Player\n! style=\"{{NBA color cell|Houston Rockets}};\"|Pos.\n! style=\"{{NBA color cell|Houston Rockets}};\"|Nationality\n! style=\"{{NBA color cell|Houston Rockets}};\"|Current team\n! style=\"{{NBA color cell|Houston Rockets}};\"|Note(s)\n! class=\"unsortable\" style=\"{{NBA color cell|Houston Rockets}};\"|Ref\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[2009 NBA draft|2009]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|2\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|34\n| {{sortname|Sergio|Llull}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|G\n| {{flagu|Spain}}\n| [[Real Madrid Baloncesto|Real Madrid]] ([[Liga ACB|Spain]])\n| Acquired from the [[Denver Nuggets]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nba.com/rockets/news/Rockets_Nab_Three_Players_in_D-317489-34.html|title=Houston purchases trio of second-round picks|date=June 26, 2009|work=NBA.com|accessdate=April 15, 2014}}</ref>\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[2008 NBA draft|2008]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|2\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|54\n| {{sortname|Maarty|Leunen}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|F\n| {{flagu|United States}}\n| [[Fortitudo Pallacanestro Bologna|Lavoropi\u00f9 Fortitudo Bologna]] ([[Serie A2 Basket|Italy]])\n| Re-acquired from the [[Dallas Mavericks]] (via [[Los Angeles Clippers|L.A. Clippers]])\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web |title=Mavericks Get Center Chinanu Onuaku in Trade With Rockets |url=https://www.nbcdfw.com/news/sports/Mavericks-Get-Center-Chinanu-Onuaku-in-Trade-With-Rockets-489926141.html |