ebruary 24, 2009}}</ref>\n\n===Basketball Hall of Famers===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! colspan=\"5\" style=\"{{NBA color cell|Houston Rockets}};\"|Houston Rockets Hall of Famers<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hoophall.com/hall-of-famers-index/|title=Hall of Famers|accessdate=February 14, 2015|work=Naismith Memorial Basketball Hall of Fame|publisher=CBS Interactive}}</ref><ref>[[#refGuide15|2015\u201316 Media Guide]], p. 149</ref>\n|-\n! colspan=\"5\" style=\"{{NBA color cell2|Houston Rockets}};\"|Players\n|-\n! No. !! Name !! Position !! Tenure !! Inducted\n|-\n| '''2'''<br />'''4''' || [[Rick Barry]] || [[Small forward|F]] || 1978\u20131980 || 1987\n|-\n| '''11'''<br />'''44''' || [[Elvin Hayes]] || [[Center (basketball)|C]]/[[Power forward (basketball)|F]] || 1968\u20131972<br />1981\u20131984 || 1990\n|-\n| '''23''' || [[Calvin Murphy]] || [[Point guard|G]] || 1970\u20131983 || 1993\n|-\n| '''24''' || [[Moses Malone]] || [[Center (basketball)|C]]/[[Power forward (basketball)|F]] || 1976\u20131982 || 2001\n|-\n| '''22''' || [[Clyde Drexler]] <sup>1</sup> || [[Shooting guard|G]]/[[Small forward|F]] || 1995\u20131998 || 2004\n|-\n| '''4''' || [[Charles Barkley]] <sup>1</sup> || [[Power forward (basketball)|F]] || 1996\u20132000 || 2006\n|-\n| '''34''' || [[Hakeem Olajuwon]] || [[Center (basketball)|C]] || 1984\u20132001 || 2008\n|-\n| '''33''' || [[Scottie Pippen]] <sup>1</sup> || [[Small forward|F]] || 1998\u20131999 || 2010\n|-\n| '''50''' || [[Ralph Sampson]] || [[Center (basketball)|C]]/[[Power forward (basketball)|F]] || 1983\u20131987 || 2012\n|-\n| '''55''' || [[Dikembe Mutombo]] || [[Center (basketball)|C]] || 2004\u20132009 || 2015\n|-\n| '''11''' || [[Yao Ming]] || [[Center (basketball)|C]] || 2002\u20132011 || 2016\n|-\n| '''1'''<br />'''3''' || [[Tracy McGrady]] || [[Shooting guard|G]]/[[Small forward|F]] || 2004\u20132010 || 2017\n|-\n! colspan=\"5\" style=\"{{NBA color cell2|Houston Rockets}};\"|Coaches\n|-\n! colspan=\"2