ll-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 2000|2000]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 2002|2002]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 2003|2003]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 2006|2006]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 2007|2007]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 2008|2008]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 2009|2009]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 2011|2011]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 2012|2012]]\n**[[Noel Skehan]] of [[Kilkenny GAA|Kilkenny]]: [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 1963|1963]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 1967|1967]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 1969|1969]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 1972|1972]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 1974|1974]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 1975|1975]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 1979|1979]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 1982|1982]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 1983|1983]]\n**[[J.J. Delaney]] of [[Kilkenny GAA|Kilkenny]]: [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 2002|2002]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 2003|2003]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 2006|2006]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 2007|2007]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 2008|2008]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 2009|2009]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 2011|2011]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 2012|2012]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 2014|2014]]\n**[[Tommy Walsh (Tullaroan hurler)|Tommy Walsh]] of [[Kilkenny GAA|Kilkenny]]: [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 2002|2002]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 2003|2003]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 2006|2006]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 2007|2007]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 2008|2008]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 2009|2009]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 2011|2011]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 2012|2012]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 2014|2014]]\n**[[Jackie Tyrrell]] of [[Kilkenny GAA|Kilkenny]]: [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 2003|2003]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 2006|2006]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 2007|2007]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 2008|2008]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 2009|2009]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 2011|2011]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 2012|2012]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 2014|2014]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 2015|2015]]\n*'''Winners of All-Ireland medals on the field of play in three decades:''':\n**[[Paddy 'Balty' Ahern]] ([[Cork GAA|Cork]]) ([[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 1919|1919]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 1926|1926]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 1927|1927]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 1929|1929]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 1931|1931]])\n**[[Frank Cummins (Kilkenny hurler)|Frank Cummins]] ([[Kilkenny GAA|Kilkenny]]) ([[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 1969|1969]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 1972|1972]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 1974|1974]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 1975|1975]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 1979|1979]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 1982|1982]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 1983|1983]])\n**[[Jimmy Doyle]] ([[Tipperary GAA|Tipperary]]) ([[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 1958|1958]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 1961|1961]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 1962|1962]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 1964|1964]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 1965|1965]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 1971|1971]])\n**[[John Doyle (hurler)|John Doyle]] ([[Tipperary GAA|Tipperary]]) ([[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 1949|1949]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 1950|1950]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 1951|1951]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 1958|1958]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 1961|1961]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 1962|1962]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 1964|1964]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 1965|1965]])\n**[[Tommy Doyle (Tipperary hurler)|Tommy Doyle]] ([[Tipperary GAA|Tipperary]]) ([[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 1937|1937]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 1945|1945]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 1949|1949]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 1950|1950]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 1951|1951]])\n**[[Declan Ryan (hurler)|Declan Ryan]] ([[Tipperary GAA|Tipperary]]) ([[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 1989|1989]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 1991|1991]], [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship 2001|2001]])\n\n====All-Ireland final appearances====\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Rank\n! Player\n! Team\n! Appearances\n! Finals\n|-\n| rowspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|1\n|[[Henry Shefflin]]\n|[[Kilkenny GAA|Kilkenny]]\n|15\n|1999, 2000, 2002, 2003, 2004, 2006, 2007, 2008, 2009, 2010, 2011, 2012 (draw), 2012 (replay), 2014 (draw), 2014 (replay).\n|-\n\n| rowspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|2\n|[[Eoin Larkin]]\n|[[Kilkenny GAA|Kilkenny]]\n|12\n|2006, 2007, 2008, 2009, 2010, 2011, 2012 (draw), 2012 (replay), 2014 (draw), 2014 (replay), 2015, 2016\n|-\n|[[J. J. Delaney]]\n|[[Kilkenny GAA|Kilkenny]]\n|12\n|2002, 2003, 2004, 2007, 2008, 2009, 2010, 2011, 2012 (draw), 2012 (replay), 2014 (draw), 2014 (replay).\n|-\n\n| rowspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|4\n|'''[[T. J. Reid]]'''\n|[[Kilkenny GAA|Kilkenny]]\n|11\n|2008, 2009, 2010, 2011, 2012 (draw), 2012 (replay), 2014 (draw), 2014 (replay), 2015, 2016, 2019\n|-\n| rowspan=\"1\