ooke]]\n|[[Limerick GAA|Limerick]]\n|1931-1938\n|[[1940 All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship|1940]]\n|{{Birth date|1914|8|16|df=yes}}\n|{{death date|2014|2|13|df=yes}} \n|{{age in years and days|1914|8|16|2014|2|13}}\n|-\n|\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[Mick Murphy (Thurles Sarsfields hurler)|Mick Murphy]]\n|[[Tipperary GAA|Tipperary]]<br>[[Clare GAA|Clare]]\n|1943-1947<br>1947-1949\n|[[1945 All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship|1945]]\n|{{Birth date|1918|8|11|df=yes}}\n|{{death date|2018|1|1|df=yes}} \n|{{age in years and days|1918|8|11|2018|1|1}}\n|-\n|\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[John T. Power]]\n|[[Kilkenny GAA|Kilkenny]]\n|1907-1925\n|[[1907 All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship|1907]], [[1911 All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship|1911]], [[1912 All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship|1912]], [[1913 All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship|1913]]\n|{{Birth date|1883|4|14|df=yes}}\n|{{death date|1982|2|1|df=yes}} \n|{{age in years and days|1883|4|14|1982|2|1}}\n|-\n|\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[Danny Ryan]]\n|[[Tipperary GAA|Tipperary]]\n|1887\n|[[1887 All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship|1887]]\n|{{Birth date|1870|4|23|df=yes}}\n|{{death date|1966|12|31|df=yes}} \n|{{age in years and days|1870|4|23|1966|12|31}}\n|-\n|\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[Larry Flaherty]]\n|[[Cork GAA|Cork]]\n|1900-1917\n|[[1903 All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship|1903]]\n|{{Birth date|1882|5|26|df=yes}}\n|{{death date|1979|1|5|df=yes}} \n|{{age in years and days|1882|5|26|1979|1|5}}\n|-\n|\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[Johnny Everard]]\n|[[Tipperary GAA|Tipperary]]\n|1950\n|[[1950 All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship|1950]]\n|{{Birth date|1924|4|16|df=yes}}\n| \n|{{age in years and days|1924|4|16}}\n|-\n|\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[Tony Reddin]]\n|[[Tipperary GAA|Tipperary]]\n|1948-1957\n|[[1949 All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship|1949]], [[1950 All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship|1950]], [[1951 All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship|1951]]\n|{{